            <h2>Investment Tips</h2>
            <p>Investing in the share market and mutual funds can be rewarding, but it requires knowledge and patience. Here are some tips for successful investing:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Diversify your portfolio to manage risk.</li>
                <li>Invest with a long-term perspective to ride out market volatility.</li>
                <li>Regularly review and rebalance your portfolio.</li>
                <li>Stay informed about market trends and company performance.</li>
                <li>Consider consulting with a financial advisor for personalized advice.</li>
